@* 
Method of passing data without using any cshtml. Set the form's action to the path you would use to navigate to your controller
just like you would in the browser. ourpage/Trip/NewTrip navigates to the NewTrip method
in the Trip controller and sends the form data as arguments to that method.
*@
<form name = "input" action = "Trip/NewTrip" method = "get">


    <select id = "Destination" name = destination>
        <option value = Upland> Upland, IN :/</option>
        <option value = Taiwan> Taiwan!</option>
    </select>
    <input name = "Destination" type = "submit" value = "Create a new Trip (html)"/>
</form>


